description: Authentic Filipino favorites are on the street food scene today! ADOruBOwl is making delicious dishes with traditional methods and ingredients, taking your taste buds on a culinary trip you'll never forget. Savory sandwiches stuffed with sisig and lumpia, and amazing rice bowls that are packed with only the best of the best ingredients are on the menu at this fantastic food truck! Dig into something great today with ADOruBOwl!
name: ADOruBOwl
